text: Marina Erakovic and Arantxa Parra Santonja were the defending champions, but chose not to participate this year. Asia Muhammad and Laura Siegemund won the title, defeating Jelena Janković and Anastasia Pavlyuchenkova in the final, 6–3, 7–5. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Topshelf Openandnbsp;- Doubles 2015 Women's Doubles
